               <h1 style="color:red; padding:2px 0px;font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif;font-size:36px;">( Symptoms )</h1>
               <p style="font-size:18px;color:rgb(253, 55, 154)">
                Distemper in dogs usually presents as yellow- to green-colored eye discharge, followed by:
               </p></div>
                <br>
                <span class="dark">Most Common Symptoms : </span>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="light"> Nasal discharge
                    </span>
                        </li>
                    <li><span class="light"> Coughing
                    </span>
                        </li>
                    <li><span class="light"> Depression
                   </span>
                        </li>
                        <li><span class="light"> Vomiting
                        </span>
                            </li>
                        <li><span class="light"> Eating less than usual
                       </span>
                            </li>
                </ul>
            <div class="text-center">
                <p style="font-size:18px;color:rgb(253, 55, 154)">
                    Some dogs only appear to have a minor cold with eye and nasal discharge, while others begin to have tremors, difficulty swallowing, or partial seizures.
As the disease progresses, dogs can develop:
                </p>
            </div>
           <br>
           <span class="dark">Other Symptoms : </span>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="light"> Chronic generalized tremors
                    </span>
                        </li>
                    <li><span class="light"> Seizures
                    </span>
                        </li>
                    <li><span class="light"> Pneumonia
                   </span>
                        </li>
                  <li><span class="light"> Crusting of the nose and foot pads
                    </span>
                        </li>
                    <li><span class="light"> Severe vomiting
                   </span>
                        </li>
                        <li><span class="light"> Diarrhea
                        </span>
                             </li>
                </ul>
